close_reason: "PR #287 review feedback addressed: exported docstring coverage no longer attributes module docs to first exports, static gate scans top-level exports and boilerplate comments more efficiently, all newly exposed declarations have specific TSDoc, focused spec/static quality pass, and direct repo coverage is 100/100/100/100."
body: ""
